{"tid":1762760,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【大陸綜藝節目】李嘉欣吳鎮宇廣東話演出楊貴妃 網民睇到爆粗起雞皮","createTime":"2019-11-29T21:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T10:23:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a322477c3a8d1fbeffcce68ade5a5e22f85075fb","tid":1762760,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:35:57.000Z","msg":"09年拍完電影《十月圍城》後，49歲的大美人李嘉欣便鮮有再參與幕前演出。早前，《延禧攻略》製作人于正宣佈李嘉欣在其製作的綜藝節目《演技派》飾演楊貴妃，而劇照一出，李嘉欣即被譽為「最靚的楊貴妃」。期待已久，李嘉欣在《演技派》中的「楊貴妃」單元今日播出，除了造形外，最令人驚喜的她與同劇中飾演唐玄宗的吳鎮宇，全程以廣東話講對白。<br />\n于正表示嘉欣是自己童年偶像，他在微博中說這個劇本專誠為嘉欣打造，而主題就是「愛一個人的感覺」，亦希望嘉欣這麼多年後以古裝出現，能令人有眼前一亮的感覺。嘉欣復出，身為小fans的于正當然隆重其事，全片雖然只有6分鐘左右，但就找來曾為《金枝慾孽》及《天與地》配樂的陳國樑。<br />\n今次這個「楊貴妃」單元，講述唐玄宗被六軍要求處死楊貴妃，而明知吳鎮宇捨不得落手的李嘉欣，就忍辱負重扮刺殺鎮宇讓對方處死自己。雖然吳鎮宇及李嘉欣今次是拍攝大陸綜藝節目，全劇人物均配上廣東話或以廣東話演出，難怪有網民看完亦留言指該片風格很像香港8、90年代的古裝電影，更有人說：「我X！粵語旁白一出來，起了一身雞皮疙瘩。」<br />\n而除了有人大讚嘉欣造形靚外，亦有不少人大讚吳鎮宇演技，更表示希望他可以演一整套劇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191129/large/1575038115_6313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191129%2Flarge%2F1575038115_6313.jpg&h=c2ab29ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191129/large/1575038115_37be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191129%2Flarge%2F1575038115_37be.jpg&h=6281a224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191129/60326158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191129%2F60326158&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=bdc8ec1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191129%2F60326158&h=a6975f57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191129/60326158</a>"},{"pid":"b307df7c4c3d1b80842add3fc0287bea7d26d480","tid":1762760,"uid":249885,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T22:16:27.000Z","msg":"點解會起雞皮"},{"pid":"997a450c619689da01aeedb7ee623bb4eaf349bd","tid":1762760,"uid":115501,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T22:41:22.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊唐玄宗"},{"pid":"60e93b3b998008c502e5c4cb6c2608d85c28ae4d","tid":1762760,"uid":37413,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣同演技有咩關係"},{"pid":"9702d4992d00da4de4cd8a6900ac41d6d0c8443c","tid":1762760,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"60e93b3b998008c502e5c4cb6c2608d85c28ae4d","tid":1762760,"uid":37413,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣同演技有咩關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90a4df792851a4cedb63486fbd531473d59723b","tid":1762760,"uid":75050,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"瘦到見骨嘅楊貴妃係邊個宇宙架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812b5ac02bf0b9267fb359d7ce9b36ffd42280de","tid":1762760,"uid":60527,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"997a450c619689da01aeedb7ee623bb4eaf349bd","tid":1762760,"uid":115501,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T22:41:22.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜你啊唐玄宗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T03:23:37.000Z","msg":"好似人地楊堅咁癡心情長劍咁，可以樣樣野都為晒伽羅去做，咁樣做對於你來講係侮辱你既智慧係戇居丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec893d28fc41431a2fbb40b35333b59bce6428c","tid":1762760,"uid":114097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b307df7c4c3d1b80842add3fc0287bea7d26d480","tid":1762760,"uid":24